## STYLE & TEXT

**风格要求**：写实摄影风格，真人照片质感，非卡通/插画/动漫风格。

- **写实摄影**：像真实高清照片，光影自然，质感真实
- **质感真实**：皮肤、头发、服饰有真实材质感，非扁平绘画感

## IDENTITY FIDELITY

The reference photo is the SOLE source of identity. All facial features, skin tone, hair, body type come from the photo — NO text descriptions override the photo.

- Face: Preserve overall structure and recognizable identity. **NO beautification** — keep natural pores, blemishes, and skin texture from photo
- Body: Maintain general body type. Natural posture, no artificial refinement
- Skin: **MUST preserve natural skin texture** — pores, blemishes, slight imperfections from reference photo
- Hair: Preserve color and style
- Recognizability: Someone who knows them should still recognize them

### Acceptable Refinements (MINIMAL)

- Remove temporary blemishes (acne, recent cuts) — **ONLY if requested**
- Soften harsh lighting shadows — without losing skin texture
- Enhance eye clarity naturally — **NO heavy eye enhancement**
- **MUST keep all permanent features**: moles, freckles, natural skin variations
- Smooth flyaway hair — **ONLY hair, NOT skin**

### NOT Acceptable (STRICT PROHIBITION)

- ❌ ANY skin smoothing or beautification
- ❌ Removing permanent features (moles, freckles, scars)
- ❌ Heavy beauty filters (plastic/doll look)
- ❌ Changing age appearance or ethnic features
- ❌ Airbrushing or poreless skin effect
- ❌ "Perfect skin" or "flawless complexion"

{{{sharedRules.facialFidelity}}}

## BODY PROPORTIONS & POSTURE

- **整体比例**：匀称自然，头身比约 1:7-1:8
- **姿态**：自然站姿，重心均匀分布，非僵硬直立或过度摆拍
- **肩部**：自然下沉，非耸肩或过度挺直
- **手臂**：自然垂于身侧，手指自然微曲
- **腿部**：自然并拢或微开，膝盖微曲（非锁死）

**NEGATIVE**: stiff posture, military stance, exaggerated pose, unnatural hand position, locked knees

